column10: I'm here & I'm #queer! Starting to line up for the Tucson Pride Parade. #lgbt #trans #girlslikeus #NCOD
Second blow up just finished. I still have my best friend and my family! Woo Hoo! #girlslikeus
Ha. My reflection today is like a bag of potatoes - lol!
